# Python Security Query Suite

# This query suite contains Python-specific security queries
# It focuses on high-impact security vulnerabilities

- description: Python Security Queries
- queries: security
- include:
    kind:
    - problem
    - path-problem
    precision:
    - high
    - very-high
    tags contain:
    - security
    - experimental

